message:
Thank you Fayetteville Police Department for hosting our Advanced Law Enforcement Human Trafficking Investigator Training Course with HTITI. We look forward to working with law enforcement officers from across the state of North Carolina for the next 3 days. 
#LEO #HelpERASE #ChildTrafficking
